<headline>Tornado Watch issued August 07 at 2:44PM EDT until August 07 at 9:00PM EDT by NWS Greenville-Spartanburg</headline>
<description>TORNADO WATCH 603 REMAINS VALID UNTIL 9 PM EDT THIS EVENING FOR
THE FOLLOWING AREAS
IN NORTH CAROLINA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 8 COUNTIES
IN PIEDMONT NORTH CAROLINA
ALEXANDER             CATAWBA               DAVIE
IREDELL               ROWAN
IN WESTERN NORTH CAROLINA
BURKE                 CALDWELL              MCDOWELL
THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF ADVANCE, ASHFORD, BETHLEHEM,
DYSARTSVILLE, ELLENDALE, FARMINGTON, FERO, FORK CHURCH, GLENWOOD,
GRANITE FALLS, HICKORY, HIDDENITE, KINGS CREEK, LENOIR, MARION,
MILLERSVILLE, MOCKSVILLE, MOORESVILLE, MORGANTON, NEBO, NEWTON,
PATTERSON, PLEASANT GROVE, SALISBURY, SAWMILLS, ST. STEPHENS,
STATESVILLE, STONY POINT, SUGAR HILL, TAYLORSVILLE, AND VALDESE.</description>
